        "text": "The following patients may be eligible for rescreening in any of the following circumstances: - A patient who has become eligible to enroll in the study as the result of a protocol amendment. - Patient status has changed such that the eligibility criterion that caused the patient to screen fail would no longer cause the patient to screen fail again. - A patient who completes screening and meets all inclusion and exclusion requirements but is unable to be enrolled due to extenuating circumstances (such as severe weather, death in family, child illness). The investigator should contact the Lilly study team prior to rescreening a patient.",
